## Prompt 7: Email & SMS Templating + Delivery

**When to use**: Week 5–6. Designs notification system.

```
I need email & SMS templating for VolunteerCalendar.org notifications.

Notifications:
1. Team Lead Review: "Hi [lead], your [ministry] schedule is ready. 
   Review & approve by [date]. [LINK]"
2. Publish Offer: "Hi [volunteer], you're scheduled for [role] on [date] 
   at [time]. Accept? Decline? [LINK]"
