2. Template engine (Handlebars, EJS, liquid?)
3. SMS design: Keep under 160 chars? or 2-message okay?
4. Delivery: Sync (real-time) vs. queue (async with Inngest/Trigger.dev)?
5. Bounce/error handling (invalid email, SMS fails)

Return: Email templates (HTML), SMS templates, delivery architecture, 
template engine selection, cost model.
```

**Expected output**: Email/SMS templates, delivery architecture, provider comparison. Implement week 5.

