## Prompt 14: Billing & Subscription Management

**When to use**: Week 7–8. Designs payment flow and tier enforcement.

```
I need to implement Stripe billing for VolunteerCalendar.org.

Tiers:
- Free: <25 vols, 1 ministry (no card required)
- Starter: $19/mo, <50 vols, 3 ministries
- Pro: $49/mo, <200 vols, unlimited ministries, analytics
