   Pro-rated? Free trial?)
3. Enforcement: At what point does overage trigger downgrade / 
   block? (Real-time check or grace period?)
4. Invoicing: Monthly or annual billing? 
   (Recommend annual discount: 20% off if yearly)
5. Downgrades: Pro → Starter. Refund prorated amount?
6. Cancellation: Keep backup of data? Delete after 30 days?

Return: Stripe billing architecture, product/pricing setup guide, 
tier enforcement logic (pseudocode), subscription state machine, 
dunning (payment failure retry) strategy.
```

**Expected output**: Stripe setup guide, billing logic, tier enforcement, payment flows. Implement weeks 7–8.

